---
const pillars = [
  { title: 'Dosage', body: 'Find the effective dose for your physiology, not a one-size protocol, so you get the benefit with less of the burden.' },
  { title: 'Timing', body: 'Align dosing with your metabolic and nutrient picture to support steady results and easier adherence.' },
  { title: 'Risk mitigation', body: 'Surface the markers that flag muscle loss, nutrient depletion, and other side-effect risks before they become problems.' },
  { title: 'Cycling off', body: 'Know the signals for when and how to taper, so progress holds instead of rebounding.' },
];
---

<section class="section glp1" id="glp1">
  <div class="container glp1__grid">
    <div class="glp1__copy">
      <p class="eyebrow" data-reveal>GLP-1, done with precision</p>
      <h2 class="glp1__title" data-reveal style="--reveal-delay: 0.06s">
        The same data, pointed at your GLP-1 results.
      </h2>
      <p class="prose" data-reveal style="--reveal-delay: 0.12s">
        GLP-1 medications work. Using them well is another matter, and most people
        are left guessing on dose, timing, and when to stop. Balance Protocol™ GPS
        reads your real biochemistry and genetics, then turns it into specific,
        personal guidance for the variables that actually move your outcome.
      </p>
      <p class="prose" data-reveal style="--reveal-delay: 0.16s">
        The result is more of the benefit, less of the risk, and a clear plan for
        what comes after.
      </p>
    </div>

    <ul class="glp1__pillars">
      {pillars.map((p, i) => (
        <li class="pillar" data-reveal style={`--reveal-delay: ${0.06 * i}s`}>
          <div class="pillar__dot" aria-hidden="true"></div>
          <h3 class="pillar__title">{p.title}</h3>
          <p class="pillar__body">{p.body}</p>
        </li>
      ))}
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .glp1 {
    background:
      radial-gradient(80% 120% at 100% 0%, oklch(28% 0.05 162 / 0.7) 0%, transparent 55%),
      var(--ink);
  }
  .glp1__grid { display: grid; gap: var(--sp-6); }
  @media (min-width: 880px) {
    .glp1__grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: var(--sp-8); align-items: start; }
    .glp1__copy { position: sticky; top: 96px; }
  }
  .glp1__title { font-size: var(--step-3); margin: var(--sp-3) 0 var(--sp-4); }

  .glp1__pillars { display: grid; gap: 1px; background: var(--line-soft); border-radius: var(--radius); overflow: hidden; border: 1px solid var(--line-soft); }
  .pillar {
    padding: var(--sp-5);
    background: var(--surface);
    position: relative;
    transition: background var(--dur-2) ease;
  }
  .pillar:hover { background: var(--surface-2); }
  .pillar__dot {
    width: 9px; height: 9px; border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--jade); box-shadow: 0 0 12px var(--jade-glow);
    margin-bottom: var(--sp-3);
  }
  .pillar__title { font-size: var(--step-1); margin-bottom: var(--sp-2); }
  .pillar__body { color: var(--muted); font-size: var(--step-0); }
  @media (min-width: 520px) {
    .glp1__pillars { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
  }
</style>
